Module java.base
Package jdk.internal.classfile

Enum Class Opcode

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Opcode>
jdk.internal.classfile.Opcode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Opcode>, Constable
public enum Opcode extends Enum<Opcode>
Describes the opcodes of the JVM instruction set, as well as a number of pseudo-instructions that may be encountered when traversing the instructions of a method.
See Also:
